narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I highly recommend this to a student who likes conducting. It's a great intro conducting course, but be prepared to be sitting around a lot waiting to conduct if the class size is large.

If you love listening to music, talking about music and learning about music, then this is a great class. It is not very much work either - but don't let that fool you. Even though it may seem not important to be diligent, it is important to hand in things on time, or your grades may suffer.
